        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I humbly suggest `ad`  for document or `af` for file: mnemonic and avoids the inconsistency of \"all lines\" instead of \"around lines\".\nWhether there can be a useful distinction between `id` and `ad`, such that the former deserves to be implemented, would be up for debate.\n",
